<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>凌雄ERP-订单管理-订单列表-打印订单</title>
    #parse("layout/header.vm")
    #parse("layout/theme.vm")

    <style>
        body {
            /*font-size: 6pt;*/
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .page {
            width:100%;
            width: 21cm;
            /*min-height: 29.7cm;*/
            min-height: 25.9cm;
            padding: 1cm 0.5cm;
            margin: 1cm auto;
            border: 1px #D3D3D3 solid;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
        }
        .printHead {
            height:1cm;
        }
        .printHead .print-col {
            height: 1cm;
            width:33.33%;
            float: left;
        }
        .printHead .print-col img {
            height:100%;
        }
        .subpage {
            padding: 0cm;
            border: 2px #666 solid;
            /*height: 280mm;*/
            height: 240mm;
            position: relative;
        }

        .printFooter {
            height:0.6cm;
        }

        @page {
            /*size: A4;*/
            size: 21cm 27.9cm;
            margin: 0;
        }

        @media print {
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                border: initial;
                border-radius: initial;
                width: initial;
                min-height: initial;
                box-shadow: initial;
                background: initial;
                page-break-after: always;
            }
            .table .bg-light {
                background-color:#FAFAFA !important;
            }

            .table-bordered > tbody > tr > td, .table>thead>tr>th {
                border: 1px solid #666 !important;
                padding: 2px 5px;
            }
            .table>thead>tr>th:first-child,
            .table-bordered > tbody > tr > td:first-child {
                border-left:0 !important;
            }

            .table>thead>tr>th:last-child,
            .table-bordered > tbody > tr > td:last-child {
                border-right:0 !important;
            }
        }

        .printH1 {
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .printH2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .qrcodeCanvas {
            height:0.8cm;
            width:0.8cm;
            float: right;
            position: absolute;
            right: 0.5cm;
            top:0.5cm;
        }

        .orderNo {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.4cm;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            right: 0.5cm;
        }

        .table .bg-light {
            background-color:#FAFAFA !important;
        }

        .table-bordered > tbody > tr > td, .table>thead>tr>th {
            border: 1px solid #666;
            padding: 2px 5px;
        }
        .table>thead>tr>th:first-child,
        .table-bordered > tbody > tr > td:first-child {
            border-left:0;
        }

        .table>thead>tr>th:last-child,
        .table-bordered > tbody > tr > td:last-child {
            border-right:0;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body style="height: auto;">
    <div class="panel">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <span class="panel-title" style="color:red;"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-print"></span>打印订单（创建21cm*27.9cm规格：控制面板=>设备和打印机=>选中当前打印机=>调整打印选项=>用户自定义打印纸），打印时候选择创建的规格，并调整打印机。</span>
        <div class="panel-header-menu pull-right mr10">
            <a href="javascript:window.print()" class="btn btn-xs btn-default btn-gradient mr5"> <i class="fa fa-print fs13"></i> </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

    <script type="text/html" id="orderBaseInfoTpl">
        {{#order}}
        <div class="row p15">
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <dl class="dl-horizontal dl-horizontal-rental mbn">
                    <dt><label>客户名称</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd class="mb5">{{buyerCustomerName}}&nbsp;</dd>

                    <dt><label>收货人</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd class="mb5">{{orderConsignInfo.consigneeName}}&nbsp;</dd>

                    <dt><label>联系方式</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd class="mb5">{{orderConsignInfo.consigneePhone}}&nbsp;</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <dl class="dl-horizontal dl-horizontal-rental mbn">
                    <dt><label>交货日期</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd class="mb5">{{#shortTime}}{{expectDeliveryTime}}{{/shortTime}}&nbsp;</dd>

                    <dt><label>起租日期</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd class="mb5">{{#shortTime}}{{rentStartTime}}{{/shortTime}}&nbsp;</dd>

                    <dt><label>备注信息</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd>{{buyerRemark}}&nbsp;</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <dl class="dl-horizontal dl-horizontal-rental mbn">
                    <dt><label>配送方式</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd class="mb5">{{deliveryModeValue}}&nbsp;</dd>

                    <dt><label>归还日期</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd>{{#shortTime}}{{expectReturnTime}}{{/shortTime}}&nbsp;</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12">
                <dl class="dl-horizontal dl-horizontal-rental mbn">
                    <dt><label>地址</label><span class="mr5">：</span></dt>
                    <dd>{{orderConsignInfo.provinceName}}{{orderConsignInfo.cityName}}{{orderConsignInfo.districtName}}{{orderConsignInfo.address}}&nbsp;</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/order}}
    </script>

